original: Lönnberg, Carl Gustaf Birger, civilingenjör, Göteborg, f. 24/12/08 i Mjölby av Birger Rudolf L. o. Sofie Eugenia Abrahamsson. — Stud:ex. i Linköp. 29, avgrex. fr. KTH 35. Lab:-chef v. Gbgs vattenverk sed. 37. Sekr. i Tekn. samf. avd. f. kemi o. fysik. Hobbies: musik o. golf.
translated: Lönnberg, Carl Gustaf Birger, civil engineer, Gothenburg, b. 24/12/08 in Mjölby to Birger Rudolf L. and Sofie Eugenia Abrahamsson. — High school graduate in Linköping in 1929, graduated from KTH in 1935. Laboratory manager at Gothenburg's waterworks since 1937. Secretary in the Technical Society's department of chemistry and physics. Hobbies: music and golf.
